{
  "stem": "1363.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were not Hungarian citizens, and already full orphans, because mother died and my brother, we had to go once a month to a building where we had to show that we are still in Hungary, that we did not escape, that the two of us are going to be called later on in time-- there was no time given, and we were hoping it never comes to it-- to go to a center.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to take us who are not citizens of Hungary, to somewhere where, as we later found out-- and we had somebody else who went there and was shot into the Russian river, Dnieper.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't whether you ever heard-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not Russian, Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't even remember where it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What they've done to these people, that they gathered them together by a few hundred.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then a train was taken, like trains to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And they were taken in those trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as far as we heard after, they had the same sort of-- finish off their life that they put them on the edge of the river and shot them in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They found their bodies after somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were the first group, Freddie and I, who had to go to this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So eventually, they said, anyone who has no Hungarian citizenship has to go here and there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And our district was in that particular area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We arrived there with our little suitcases, toothbrush, pajama, one-day clothing change.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they kept us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they kept us there for weeks on end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "16.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
